Package: viewports
Type: Package
Title: ALTREP implementation of viewports peering into sections of vectors
Description: An ALTREP implementation of viewports which emulate a subset of other vectors and, when retrieving
             elements, they translate the indices into the source vector's indices and retrieve elements from there.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Konrad",  family = "Siek", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "siekkonr@fit.cvut.cz"))
Maintainer: Konrad Siek <siekkonr@fit.cvut.cz>
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
NeedsCompilation: yes

